{"tid":777441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[原告變被告]旺角表演者轉戰天星爆衝突　民建聯區議員譴責示威者","createTime":"2018-08-13T02:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T02:51:57.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f361f2cadc15bdaf855839fd0a651245a5d5064c","tid":777441,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180813/s00001/1534124421159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180813%2Fs00001%2F1534124421159&d=QwPp060cUdNSOk1CN8PejP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3180a611\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180813%2Fs00001%2F1534124421159&h=4c594394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180813/s00001/1534124421159</a><br />\n<br />\n旺角行人專用區「殺街」後，天星碼頭外空地日前爆發示威者與表演者衝突，有「大媽」表演團隊由警方陪同離場，免生混亂。油尖旺區議會主席民建聯葉傲冬今早在商台節目譴責示威者手法，「（香港）有示威集會自由，但明顯是挑釁行為，只為增加衝突，對事件無幫助」。<br />\n<br />\n葉傲冬表示，過去兩個周確有有旺角表演者轉到天星碼頭，惟數量、表演人數及模式都與旺角不同，而他到現場視察，形容聲浪比旺角細小。<br />\n<br />\n問到現在情況是否可以接受，葉傲冬形容表演團體及表演者「一路都有變化」，須再觀察運作模式。他續說，香港有表演自由，應思考「如何令大家相對接受到成件事」。"},{"pid":"cbac0ae5fb61125591448e1be434f60526c761bb","tid":777441,"uid":67237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"淫賤聯真係好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"e89766f655b96460faf2fdc7b421789a7a3a28b6","tid":777441,"uid":134630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩, 要個議員日日去個度開工10個鐘丫<br />\n睇佢頂唔頂得順<br />\n有冇諗過附近冇得揀既商鋪呀屌你<br />\n呢班撚樣唔會比稅架<br />\n就算唔企係班示威者角度諗<br />\n都諗下班會交稅既商鋪諗下喇"},{"pid":"da2efd02c0db6d123eeda8c86b45303be9d13a9a","tid":777441,"uid":152476,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"證明班大媽妖孽真係做緊政治任務，搞臭香港"},{"pid":"a14b7b50ce784b27b2ef0fa0917886355a2c3dfc","tid":777441,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"乜有人預佢會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bbbf98683174fb6e7953e0a12e9c68aba1e36a","tid":777441,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cf91900946f69dab4397e2af42b5a44e4ed738","tid":777441,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"扮咩現場視察丫，自己睇開大媽舞咋嘛"}]}